# == Class: profile::mcollective::server
#
# Profile for an mcollective server node.
# Server in this case indicates a node that is managed by mcollective.
#
# === Parameters
#
# None
#
# === Variables
#
# None
#
# === Examples
#
# include profile::mcollective::server
#
